snippet.title: Arcade Game: Mad Crasher (1984 SNK)
snippet.description:
A diagonal driving/shooting 'em up game.

This was SNK's first 3-D Isometric game.

Note: Used Invincibility cheat and infinite lives cheat after down to last life. The game is endless so I quit afterwards.
